Assume "students" is a collection


1. Remove all the documents from collection
    db.students.remove()
    
2. Remove single document from collection
    db.students.remove({id : 10},1)    // 1 refer single document

3. Delete one document from collection
    db.orders.deleteOne( { "client" : "Crude Traders Inc." })
    
    
4. Delete many docuemnts from collection
    db.orders.deleteMany( { "client" : "Crude Traders Inc." })

5. Find one document and delete from collection
    db.scores.findOneAndDelete(
      { "name" : "M. Tagnum" }
    )
    
